          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where else can I buy BERO?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We want to make it easy for people to find and enjoy BERO. We will continue working hard to add more locations to our <a href=\"/pages/where-to-find-us\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Where to find us\">store locator</a>, so our consumers are able to purchase BERO at their favorite stores, restaurants, and bars. Keep an eye out for updates on our website and social (<a href=\"https://instagram.com/berobrewing\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">@berobrewing</span></a>).</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_bNUNcC": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is BERO available in restaurants / venues?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We want to make it easy for people to find and enjoy BERO. We will continue working hard to add more locations to our <a href=\"/pages/where-to-find-us\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Where to find us\">store locator</a>, so our consumers are able to purchase BERO at their favorite restaurants and bars. Keep an eye out for updates on our website and social (<a href=\"https://instagram.com/berobrewing\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">@berobrewing</span></a>).</p>",
            "page": "",
