    "pbj_collapsible_content_N49mm6": {
      "type": "pbj-collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_BiDpXg": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I join Club BERO?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>You can sign up as a Free Member with as little as your name, email, and address, or join our BEROMASTER tier for a $55 annual membership fee. Visit our Club BERO page to <a href=\"/pages/loyalty\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Loyalty\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">sign up</span>.</a></p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_diUe3Q": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I earn credits?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>By purchasing any BERO 6-pack or Variety Pack online or in-store. Club BERO Free Members receive $0.25 credit for each 6-pack purchased. BEROMASTER members receive double the credit at $0.50 credit for each 6-pack purchase. </li><li>By purchasing BERO Collection items online. Club BERO Free Members receive a $1 credit for every $30 of BERO Collection items purchased. BEROMASTER members receive double the credit at $2 credit for every $30 of BERO Collection items purchased. </li><li>There are other ways to earn credits if you are a Club BERO member—such as referrals, reviews, social follows, and more. Members can see a full list of credit-earning actions in their dashboard.</li></ul>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_WbRMkh": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do I get credits from products purchased in stores?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We value our customers and their loyalty, no matter where they choose to shop. Our industry-leading loyalty program rewards you for every BERO pack purchase, wherever you buy. Once you join Club BERO (with either a <a href=\"/pages/loyalty\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Loyalty\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">free or paid membership</span></a>), simply scan the unique QR code inside any BERO 6-pack or Variety Pack. You'll earn credits on every purchase, which you can redeem on your next <a href=\"http://www.berobrewing.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.berobrewing.com</span></a> purchase.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_RYUCQJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I redeem my credits in-store?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>What matters most to us is making it easy for you to find BERO and be rewarded for your loyalty. We're actively working on ways to help our loyal customers redeem their BERO credits wherever it’s most convenient. Stay tuned for updates on our website and social channels (<a href=\"https://instagram.com/berobrewing\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">@berobrewing</span></a>), and in the meantime, don’t hesitate to redeem your credits on <a href=\"http://www.berobrewing.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.berobrewing.com</span></a>.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_8BV8gU": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where can I find my code?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>On the inside of any BERO 6-pack or Variety Pack, you will find a sticker that looks like this:</li></ul><p></p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_Amga6K": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does it take for credits to appear in my account?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Credits will appear in your Club BERO account immediately and automatically. The best part is you can use them on your next order.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_TXMMpc": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What rewards can I get?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Rewards depend on your membership tier. For more information on membership tiers and benefits, <a href=\"/pages/loyalty\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Loyalty\">check out Club BERO here.</a></p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_A8e8Gf": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I track my credits?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>You can see your Club BERO credit balance at any time by logging in to your account dashboard. <a href=\"/pages/account-club-bero\" target=\"_blank\">Sign in here.</a></p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_ewpf6U": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I claim my credits for my offline BERO purchases?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Here are the steps to claim your credits and add them to your account:</p><ul><li>Scan the QR code or <a href=\"/pages/qr-claim\">enter your QR code manually here.</a></li><li>Login to or create your Club BERO account (you don’t have to be a paid member to claim credits). <a href=\"/pages/account-club-bero\">Sign in or sign up here.</a></li><li>If the code has not been claimed already, your credits will be automatically added to your account.</li></ul><p>You use and redeem your credits immediately on <a href=\"http://www.berobrewing.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.berobrewing.com.</span></a></p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_t86jrP": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I redeem my credits?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Here are the steps to redeem your credits:</p><ul><li>Log in to your Club BERO account dashboard (you don’t have to be a paid member to redeem credits). <a href=\"/pages/account-club-bero\" target=\"_blank\">Sign in here.</a></li><li>Click on “redeem credits”.</li><li>Enter the amount of credits you want to redeem from your available credit balance.</li><li>A unique discount code for that amount will be generated and can be automatically applied to your cart if you choose to do so</li><li>Fill your cart with all your favorite BERO beers and BERO Collection items and checkout with your savings applied.</li></ul>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_nLU6hd": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do my Club BERO credits and status expire?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>Free Membership is for life and does not expire. </li><li>BEROMASTER membership is a one-year membership that will auto-renew.</li><li>Credits will remain active for 12 months from earning them. But, don’t worry. All members will be notified of credit expiration timelines in advance.</li></ul>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_ULtDTg": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do I lose my credits if I cancel my Club BERO membership?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Your credits are yours. You will maintain access to your earned credits even if you don’t have an active membership or have canceled your membership. Your credits will remain active for 12 months from earning them.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_3FmD8g": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What happens to my credits if I cancel a BERO order or return BERO Collection items?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>If you placed an order on <a href=\"https://www.berobrewing.com\">www.berobrewing.com</a> and:</li><li><strong>Cancel the order</strong> OR <strong>get a full refund for your order</strong>, your Club BERO credits earned for that specific order will no longer be applied to your account (applicable for beer and BERO collection items). </li><li><strong>Get a partial refund for your order</strong>, only the equivalent Club BERO credits will be deducted from your account.</li></ul><p>Please reach out to our customer service team at <a href=\"mailto:support@bero.com\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">support@berobrewing.com</span></a>. if you have any questions. </p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_y3QYB8": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is Club BERO the same as a subscription?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>No, Club BERO is not the same as a subscription program. Club BERO is a membership loyalty program that gives you instant rewards and exclusive access to a range of benefits and savings. You don’t need to commit to a specific purchase frequency to be part of Club BERO! <a href=\"/pages/loyalty\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Loyalty\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Learn more about Club BERO.</span></a></p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_e7qgFm": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will my BEROMASTER membership renew automatically?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, your BEROMASTER membership will renew automatically on an annual basis.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_dTPV8H": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I cancel my annual membership?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>While BEROMASTER memberships are non-refundable—given the immediate value you receive upon purchase—you can cancel at any time by emailing <a href=\"mailto:cancelmembership@bero.com\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">cancelmembership@berobrewing.com</span></a>, so your membership does not renew. Access to your BEROMASTER benefits will remain active until the end of the billing cycle.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        }
