    "pbj_collapsible_content_WybYU4": {
      "type": "pbj-collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_9HxfRY": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I unsubscribe from BERO newsletter and texts?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>The last thing we want to do is be a bother and we work hard to limit the number of messages we send. However, if you do wish to unsubscribe, you can use the “unsubscribe” link at the bottom of our emails at any time, reply “STOP” to any SMS, or login to your account and adjust your communication preferences.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_BRxqP7": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I refer a friend?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<ul><li>If you are a Club BERO member (free or paid), you can email someone your unique referral code directly from the referral page in your account dashboard—or manually copy and paste your link and share. This will unlock an immediate credit reward for the member! </li></ul><p>If you are not a Club BERO member, you can visit <a href=\"http://www.berobrewing.com/pages/referrals\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">www.berobrewing.com/pages/referrals</span></a> to create your own referral smart link to send to someone.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_XWgwMk": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I use a gift card?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Cheers on receiving a BERO gift card. To use it, enter the unique code associated with your gift card in the discount field at checkout. If the balance available on your gift card is greater than or equal to your order total, then you can complete your order. If the balance available on your gift card is less than your order total, you will need to enter an additional payment method for the balance of the order value before you can complete checkout. This includes adding another gift card.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_c6rXkp": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do gift cards expire?",
            "open_collapsible": false,
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our BERO gift cards expire 5 years from the date of purchase. We encourage you to use your gift card within this timeframe to ensure you can enjoy everything BERO has to offer. If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to <a href=\"mailto:support@bero.com\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">support@berobrewing.com</span></a>.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "anchor": ""
          }
        }
      },
